chan = Rails.configuration.slack_channels.horizons_arcana

header "🔮 welcome to arcana!"

section <<~TEXT, markdown: true
  You've just been added to <##{chan}>, the channel for Horizons Arcana in Singapore! For more info, check out [horizons.hackclub.com/arcana](https://horizons.hackclub.com/arcana).

  Head over and introduce yourself!
TEXT
